### PUT /api/v1/admin/tariffs/{id}
### Descripción: Actualizar plan de tarifa. Requiere Admin/Support + X-Tenant-Id.
### Headers requeridos: Authorization: Bearer <token>, X-Tenant-Id: <guid>
### Códigos: 200 OK (TariffPlanDto) | 404 TARIFF_NOT_FOUND | 403 cross-tenant | 400

# @name updateTariff
PUT {{BASE_URL}}/api/v1/admin/tariffs/{{TARIFF_ID}}
Authorization: Bearer {{ACCESS_TOKEN}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{TENANT_ID}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Standard Updated",
  "currency": "USD",
  "baseFare": 5.50,
  "pricePerKm": 1.60,
  "pricePerMinute": 0.30,
  "minimumFare": 9.00,
  "effectiveFromUtc": null
}

### Response esperado (200): TariffPlanDto
### Response error (404): { "error", "code": "TARIFF_NOT_FOUND" }
### Response error (403): Forbid (TARIFF_CROSS_TENANT)
